# ====================================
# Setup Instructions:
# ====================================
#
# 1. Copy this file to .env:
#    cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Create a Supabase project at https://supabase.com
#
# 3. Update VITE_SUPABASE_URL and VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#
# 4. Run the SQL migration from supabase/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql
#    in the Supabase SQL Editor
#
# 5. Enable the following in Supabase Dashboard:
#    - Authentication > Email provider
#    - Realtime > Enable for all tables
#    - Storage > Create buckets: avatars, quiz-images, media, documents
#
# 6. For Yandex Cloud deployment:
#    - Create Object Storage bucket
#    - Set up Cloud Functions
#    - Configure CDN
#    - Update the bucket and region variables above
